org.yamcs.algorithms

Class AbstractAlgorithmExecutor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.yamcs.algorithms.AbstractAlgorithmExecutor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AlgorithmExecutor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MathAlgorithmExecutor, ScriptAlgorithmExecutor

    public abstract class AbstractAlgorithmExecutor
extends Object
implements AlgorithmExecutor
    Skeleton implementation for algorithms conforming to the XTCE Algorithm definition. - it collects all the inputs into an inputList and implements the triggering based on the mandatory parameters.
